{"tid":114853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一連三晚！江蘇工廠起火","createTime":"2017-02-10T06:16:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T06:45:39.000Z","uid":32407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dcdae662405cc64439f10b50e37048abab202415","tid":114853,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T06:16:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170209/bkncn-20170209230608676-0209_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170209%2Fbkncn-20170209230608676-0209_05011_001.html&d=hvrwae4HshPHSMms9GCCYCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=0d16fb66\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170209/bkncn-20170209230608676-0209_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170209/photo/bkncn-20170209230608676-0209_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170209%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170209230608676-0209_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=35703211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地一連3晚爆出工廠大火！繼前晚山西呂梁金屬鎂廠爆炸及昨晚安徽銅陵化工廠巨爆後，江蘇杭集一間工廠，今晚8時40分許亦發生大火。從網傳片段所見，現場火勢猛烈，濃煙不斷升上半空。<br />\n<br />\n當地居民表示，起火工廠為威力克酒店用品廠，大火疑與廠前的紙箱起火有關。另有網民指，有孔明燈從空中掉到工廠，結果引發大火。消防部門已趕到現場滅火，暫未傳出有人員傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67565040ff688bc5ba607c4cb4ee4a5e6fee8915","tid":114853,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T06:17:14.000Z","msg":"唔通有內鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1909e5f64d94384d110a6b3798a4fd1861d129d2","tid":114853,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T06:17:58.000Z","msg":"Claim 保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7f813ca3d1f2c2fd66baa928f4b9